						<h4>The newspaper that #MeToo missed</h4>
						<h2>By Jennifer Robison</h2></a>
					</div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://www.cjr.org/special_report/sheldon-adelson-metoo-las-vegas-review-journal.php/" style="z-index:1 !important;"><span class="link-spanner"></span></a>
